#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/07_The_Book_of_Crelanu.cfg:106
msgid "Following ancient signs, Gwiti and Arkal-Thil arrive at a cramped, shadowed cave passage. Even their dark vision is limited by the oppressive gloom surrounding them."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/07_The_Book_of_Crelanu.cfg:115
msgid "So, we’re finally here... the resting place of Crelanu’s tome, hidden beyond these darkness."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/07_The_Book_of_Crelanu.cfg:119
msgid "It feels different, master — colder, and something... alive? This place seems to push back against us."
