#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/07_The_Book_of_Crelanu.cfg:140
msgid "<i>At the far end of the cave, a massive stone wall marked with ancient runes blocks the way forward. The runes pulse faintly, their magical seals still strong after centuries.</i>"
